attributes.title: absolute garbage
attributes.review: as soon as i opened the app i vomited. maybe it’s the terrible way the app is set up, maybe it was because of the fact that i ate a whole block of cheese- we’ll never know. after that i tried to close the app to calm my stomach down but it wouldn’t close. i say there for a solid two minutes gagging because i had to continue looking at the disgusting cheeto before the app finally crashed. it’s safe to say i would NOT recommend this to anyone who wants to have a good day.
